2:T720,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Cohere better than Inflection?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Cohere scores 7.0 overall while Inflection scores 6.0. Cohere is best for enterprise RAG and developers, while Inflection excels for enterprise and custom AI assistants."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Cohere or Inflection?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Cohere starts at Free and Inflection starts at Enterprise. Cohere offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Cohere to Inflection?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Cohere and Inflection support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Cohere vs Inflection?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Cohere holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10. Inflection has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Cohere for excellent retrieval-augmented generation and Inflection for enterprise-grade security and reliability."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Cohere or Inflection?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Cohere for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Inflection remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize enterprise-grade security and reliability. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$",